Dude Perfect: The Hero Tour Fan Early Access Event
A brand-new, immersive experience designed for families and superfans to see The Dudes up close like never before. Be a part of the Dudes’ sold-out Hero Tour with the best seat in the house in the first-ever cinematic look. The show is full of action-packed battles, classic segments, and exclusive backstage access. Even if you have been to the show, you've never seen Dude Perfect like this!

! PAGE CONTENT ==========================================
! CORPORATE EVENTS ==========================================
==========================================
Corporate events
We can help with that whole work/life balance thing. Whether you’re team-building, hosting an off-site, celebrating a company milestone, or just looking to get out of the office, we’ll make sure everyone on your team has a good time.
Private event rooms can host up to 60 people
Cater your event from our full food and beverage menu
Customize your itinerary with games, bowling, movies, and more
Pre-paid game cards so everyone can play ASAP
AV & tech hookups for presentations and meetings
Off-site anytime — book us during the work week or after hours
Book Now
hky-text-image
! ADULT FRIENDLY EVENTS ==========================================
==========================================
Adult-friendly events
If you’re hosting game night, ladies night, a gender-reveal party, a graduation party, your fantasy draft, or a family reunion, we promise it’ll be way more fun if you do it with us. We’ve got packages for whatever you’re celebrating.
Party host to accommodate all your needs
Customize your itinerary with games, bowling, movies, and more
Food and drink tickets available, including alcohol
Pre-paid game cards so everyone can play ASAP
Private rooms available
Rooms equipped with screens so you can show videos, slideshows, or watch the game
Book Now

Birthday parties
Let the kids do their thing while you do yours. We’ve got everything you need to hear “Remember the year we played Hooky?” for years to come.
Party host to accommodate all your needs
Private rooms that host up to 30 guests (can be combined for larger parties)
Customize your itinerary with games, bowling, movies, and more
Pre-paid game cards so everyone is loaded up and ready to play
Cater your event from our full food and beverage menu
BYOCake!

! PRIVATE MOVIE SCREENINGS ==========================================
! Image

Private movie screenings
Get off your screens — ours are way better! Book an entire theater for your friends, family, rec league, or coworkers and experience the big screen all to yourselves. Whether you want to watch a new release or one of your all-time favorites, we’ll bring the movie magic.
Rent any of our theaters for a private viewing experience
Theaters that fit small and large parties
Full in-theater food, beverage, and cocktail service
Dedicated party host to give your experience the Hollywood treatment
Keep the good times going and combine with bowling, games, and more
Book Now

When’s the last time you played Hooky?
Everyone needs an escape from their routine from time to time. A place where you can catch a movie, bowl a perfect game, get a bite to eat, grab a drink, play games, throw a party, throw darts, and get lost in endless other activities and fun with all your favorite people. This is that place. So what are you waiting for? Ditch the everyday and come play Hooky!
Visit Us
